title: Morellas Forest Discography 1995-2002 (5 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
MORELLAS FOREST DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 5 releases...

 * 1995 - Hang-Out
 * 1995 - Super Deluxe
 * 1996 - Ultraphonic Hiss
 * 1998 - From Dayton With Love
 * 2002 - Tiny Lights Of Heaven

Morella's Forest was a band from Dayton, Ohio which formed in 1992. They released three albums on Tooth and Nail Records and one with an independent label. Their signature sound is noise pop or space music comparable to Starflyer 59 or The Breeders.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
